This is the source of UTF8-CPP (<http://utfcpp.sourceforge.net/>),
version 2.3.4. The following changes have been applied:

Changes:
========

- Changed include paths to point to the correct files
  within our source tree
- Replaced uint_8/uint16_t/uint32_t typedefs by including
  src/common/types.h instead
- Silenced compiler warnings about variable shadowing
- Removed Windows-style line endings

See also utf8cpp.patch for details.
